subject: ENGLISH
text: Punctuate the following passage correctly and rewrite it as two stanzas of rhyming verse. Put the following sentence into reported speech. What is the origin of the following idioms: To kill the fatted calf, a Judas kiss, a Herculean task, to cross the Rubicon, the Slough of Despond?
